<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <h1 class="hero-headline">From ticket to PR</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      Agent Smith is an open source AI coding agent. You drop a ticket into your tracker, it clones the repo into a sandbox, writes the code, runs the tests, opens the PR, and sets the ticket back to resolved.
    </p>
    <p class="hero-sub hero-sub-secondary">
      Every run shows its cost. Every change comes with the reasoning the agent followed.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="{{ site.docsUrl }}/get-it-running/install/" class="btn btn-primary">Get started</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/{{ site.githubRepo }}" class="btn btn-tertiary">View on GitHub</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-meta">
      <div class="hero-meta-item">
        <a href="https://github.com/{{ site.githubRepo }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" aria-hidden="true" width="14" height="14"><path d="M8 .25a.75.75 0 0 1 .673.418l1.882 3.815 4.21.612a.75.75 0 0 1 .416 1.279l-3.046 2.97.719 4.192a.75.75 0 0 1-1.088.791L8 12.347l-3.766 1.98a.75.75 0 0 1-1.088-.79l.72-4.194L.818 6.374a.75.75 0 0 1 .416-1.28l4.21-.611L7.327.668A.75.75 0 0 1 8 .25z" fill="currentColor"/></svg>
          <span id="gh-stars">—</span> stars
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-meta-item">MIT licensed</div>
      <div class="hero-meta-item">Runs on your infrastructure</div>
      <div class="hero-meta-item">Calls your AI provider directly</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-mockup">
    <img src="lifecycle.svg" alt="A ticket comes in from your tracker. Agent Smith spawns one sandbox per repo, drives a tool-calling loop, then opens one PR per repo and resolves the ticket." loading="eager" />
  </div>
</section>
